[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    855[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206m  "narrative_summary": "Dermatology provider billing meaningful volumes of physical-therapy CPT codes (97110, 97112, 97140). Codes are not typically billed by dermatology practices. Could indicate aesthetic/laser services being miscoded, a legitimate ancillary service line, or billing error. Recommend clinical review before payment integrity escalation.",[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    856[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206m  "status": "new",[K
