[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    118[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mThis is the same diagram and orchestration flaw flagged in Recipe 2.6 expert review and Recipe 2.7 expert review. Recipe 2.8 resolved its diagram. Recipe 2.10 expert review surfaced the same finding as A1 with the same priority. The fix template exists.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    119[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    120[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m  [38;2;191;97;106mFor a CDS recipe specifically, the stakes are clinical-safety-critical. The Step 9 validation failure modes the architecture is built to catch include: [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140msafety_finding_not_represented[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (a deterministic interaction or contraindication finding that the model dropped), [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mdose_not_in_structured_source[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (a fabricated dose), [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcontradicts_contraindication[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (a recommended drug for which the safety-check found a contraindication), [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mcontradicts_allergy[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (a recommended drug that conflicts with a documented allergy), [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mdirective_language_in_model_voice[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (a regulatory-posture violation that erodes the FDA CDS exemption), [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mout_of_scope[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m (a recommendation outside the intended CDS surface). The recipe's "Failure Modes You Have to Design Around" subsection specifically names "missed interaction," "missed contraindication," and "fabricated dose or dosing frequency" as the outcomes the architecture is built to prevent. The orchestrator is the last gate between a flagged synthesis and the clinician UI, and the diagram (and the implied pseudocode sequencing) depicts that gate as absent. A clinician-facing CDS surface delivering a synthesis where the validator caught a contraindication-conflict is precisely the safety-rail bypass the architecture exists to prevent.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    121[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mFix:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m Make three changes in lockstep:[K
