[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    310[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mS1 (PHI minimization in the synthesis prompt) and A2 (synthesis-run idempotency) do not conflict but are independent edits at adjacent stages of the pipeline. S1 is a one-paragraph minimization step between Step 2 and Step 8; A2 is a deterministic-event-key change at Step 1. They compose cleanly with no ordering constraint between them. Both are recurring chapter-wide patterns (S1 from 2.7/2.8/2.10; A2 from 2.4 through 2.10).[K
